      • updateJobsWpsGroupName

        public void updateJobsWpsGroupName(String oldWpsIdentifier,
                          String newWpsIdentifier)
                            throws org.quartz.SchedulerException
        All of the jobs' groupnames with the groupname "oldWpsIdentifier" will be updated to the groupnames of newWpsIdentifier. New jobs will be created and registred in the scheduler to make this possible. After that triggers will be regenerated and added to the new job. The old ones will be removed.
        Parameters:
        oldWpsIdentifier - Old name to identify the Jobs
        newWpsIdentifier - New name which will replace the old one
        Throws:
        org.quartz.SchedulerException
